OL,3,C'Better days will come': Lily on her
OL,4,Cnew life as a quadruple amputee
OL,6,FShe explains: "I would like to get
OL,7,Fback to it. Cardiff Uni have offered
OL,8,Fme a place to continue if I want to
OL,9,Fnext September, so if I'm in the right
OL,10,Fposition with rehab I would love to do
OL,11,Fthat.
OL,13,F"I'm faced with lots of things I can't
OL,14,Fdo, everything is more challenging -
OL,15,Fhopefully that won't always be the
OL,16,Fcase and I'm committed to becoming as
OL,17,Findependent as possible."
