OL,3,C'Better days will come': Lily on her
OL,4,Cnew life as a quadruple amputee
OL,6,FLily continues: "When I look back at
OL,7,Fphotos of how I looked nine months
OL,8,Fago, I loved my long hair and I think
OL,9,Fhow I'm going to look so different.
OL,11,F"The scarring - it's hard enough being
OL,12,Fa young woman in this day and age,
OL,13,Faccepting your body image without
OL,14,Fhaving amputation, so it's a long
OL,15,Fprocess.
OL,17,F"My partner says my brain and my heart
OL,18,Fare still the same, so I'm lucky to
OL,19,Fhave them."
