OL,3,C'Better days will come': Lily on her
OL,4,Cnew life as a quadruple amputee
OL,6,FA fundraising page was set up to let
OL,7,Fpeople donate towards Lily's
OL,8,Fprosthetics, physiotherapy,
OL,9,Frehabilitation, and any adaptations
OL,10,Fshe may need to her living
OL,11,Fenvironment. It has already raised
OL,12,Fnearly #500,000.
OL,14,FLily says she has been "overwhelmed"
OL,15,Fby the support.
