OL,3,C'Better days will come': Lily on her
OL,4,Cnew life as a quadruple amputee
OL,6,FShe explains: "I can't believe it, I
OL,7,Fwonder why so many people want to
OL,8,Fsupport me in that way. I'll be
OL,9,Fforever grateful, it opens a lot of
OL,10,Fdoors which might not have been
OL,11,Fpossible."
OL,13,FLily enjoyed being active before her
OL,14,Fillness and hopes to get that feeling
OL,15,Fback when she can.
OL,17,FShe adds: "I've always loved swimming
OL,18,Fand being in the sea. As soon as my
OL,19,Fskin heals, I'll be getting back in
OL,20,Fthat pool."
